## Critical rules

- **NEAREST sampling**: Never use linear filtering on pixel art
- **No upscale**: Atlas stays at native 512×{h}. GPU NEAREST handles magnification
- **Crop feet to bottom**: Vertical crop removes transparent padding so feet touch ground
- **Alpha pipeline**: RGBA PNG → Blender Alpha → glTF → Rgba8UnormSrgb → ALPHA_BLENDING → discard < 0.35
- **Direction offset +4**: Shader adds 4 to dir_idx so camera-north shows front sprite
- **include_bytes!**: GLB is embedded at compile time. Must rebuild WASM after any GLB change
- **Cache bust**: Static server caches aggressively. Use `?v=Date.now()` or hard-refresh
